data.description: I'm A Gorgeous Custom Built Home.  Built in 1996. Authentic Spanish Style Home with lots of upgrades. Home features wrap around porch with huge outside patio area with view. Marble fireplace with 15 foot ceilings in living room. Master Bedroom sits at the highest portion of house with an outdoor balcony with a wonderful view of the mountains to the North. On the main level of the house you have a beautiful gourmet kitchen with Viking appliances.  Below the main level of house you have two additional bedrooms and a bathroom. Lots of light, bright , and airy feel to this custom home. Mission Tile Roof, Spanish Lace Stucco on the exterior of house makes it truly an authentic Spanish feel. Home has R.V. Access off of Ghent. This home has a view from every room.  There is also an area under house that can be used as storage or better yet a wine storage area with heavy duty door for security.
